	<div id="rightColumn">
		<a name="44"></a><h5><br>News</h5><p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><strong>Uni-Verse Release 3</strong></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>March 15, 2007</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The Uni-Verse Consortium is happy to announce its third public <a href="Downloads.58.0.html" target="_top" >release of software</a> in binary format. Quality should have been improved dramatically. </p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><strong>Uni-Verse at IST Event 2006</strong></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>November 21-23, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The Uni-Verse project is exhibiting at the <a href="http://europa.eu.int/information_society/istevent/2006/index_en.htm">IST Event 2006</a> in Helsinki, Finland November 21-23.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">For the first time we will show the unique acoustic simulation.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><strong>Uni-Verse at SIGRAD Conference</strong></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>November 22-23, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">A paper on the design of Verse will be presented at the <a href="http://www.sigrad.se/">SIGRAD</a> conference in Skövde, Sweden</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">November 22-23. The last part of the talk will cover the use of Verse for content creation in the game industry.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="SIGGRAPH_2006.67.0.html" target="_top"><strong>SIGGRAPH Success</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>August 18, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The SIGGRAPH was a big success for the Uni-Verse project. Here are some images taken on the show floor, showing the booth where Uni-Verse was displayed.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="Movies.66.0.html" target="_top"><strong>Uni-Verse Presentation Movie</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>August 17, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">A Uni-Verse presentation movie made by our partner Paregos had premiere at SIGGRAPH in Boston and was highly appreciated by the audience. </p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://www.siggraph.org/s2006/"><strong>Uni-Verse at SIGGRAPH</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>July 6, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">Uni-Verse will have a booth in the <a href="http://esub.siggraph.org/cgi-bin/cgi/idEDetail.html&amp;CompanyID=1128">Open Source Pavilion</a> at the SIGGRAPH tradeshow, August 1-3 in Boston. See you there!</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://www.siggraph.org/s2006/main.php?f=conference&amp;p=birds"><strong>Verse BOF at SIGGRAPH</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>July 6, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">Eskil Steenberg, the designer of the <a href="http://verse.blender.org/">Verse protocol</a>, will lead a Verse BOF at SIGGRAPH, August 1, 1-2 pm, Boston Convention and Exhibition Center, Room 213.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="Downloads.58.0.html" target="_top"><strong>Uni-Verse Software Release</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>March 15, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The Uni-Verse Consortium is happy to announce its first public release of software in binary format. If you are interested in our work, feel free to download and try these out!</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://orange.blender.org" target="_top"><strong>Orange Open Movie Premiere</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>February 24, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The premiere of <em>Elephants Dream</em>, the Orange Open Movie project, will take place on March 24, 2006 in Amsterdam. <em>Elephants Dream</em> is a co-production of the Blender Foundation and the Netherlands Media Art Institute.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://www.youris.com/video.cfm?video=60&amp;rubrique=2#" target="_top"><strong>Uni-Verse now on video</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>February 20, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">A video on the Uni-Verse project is free for ordering, including for broadcasting by TV stations. Background information and Beta SP/Num tape can be ordered online.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://lwn.net/Articles/171321/" target="_top"><strong>Verse in Linux Weekly News</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>February 16, 2006</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The February 16, 2006 issue of Linux Weekly News mentions Verse in an article titled "Toward a free metaverse". </p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><strong>IST TV</strong></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>December 1, 2005</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The Uni-Verse project has been chosen to be featured by the IST TV project for the production of a promotional video. Shooting took place October 26-28, 2005 in Stockholm and Amsterdam at the sites of partners II, KTH and Blender Foundation.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://www.intuition2005.org" target="_top" ><strong>Poster at Intuition 2005</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>November 24-25, 2005</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">Lauri Savioja from HUT and Gert Svensson from KTH present a poster on Uni-Verse at the 2nd Intuition Workshop in Paris, France.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://purple.blender.org/cms/About_Purple.572.0.html" target="_top" ><strong>Purple released</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>October 31, 2005</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">"Purple" is a development platform, to develop a plug-in based "computational engine" for Verse.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://www.blender.org/cms/Verse-Blender.verse_blender.0.html" target="_top" ><strong>Blender-Verse testbuild</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>October 15, 2005</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">The 3D Tool Blender released a testing version with integrated Verse Protocol.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><a href="http://www.blender.org/cms/Emil_Brink.686.0.html" target="_top" ><strong>Verse Presentations</strong></a></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;"><em>October 10, 2005</em></p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">Emil Brink and Eskil Steenberg talked about the latest development on the 4th annual Blender Conference.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 0 0;">&nbsp;</p>
